        fr: { headline: 'A new journey is about to begin.', symbol: 'The Fool stands at the cliff\'s edge, eyes skyward, full of innocent hope. His white rose symbolizes untouched potential. This card in the present position signals that a new chapter is opening in your life. The energy of fresh beginnings surrounds you right now.', advice: 'Trust your instincts over perfect preparation. The courage to take the first step is what creates the path.' },
